rtd->cpu_dais/codec_dais are set at soc_new_pcm_runtime().
rtd->num_cpus/codecs should be set there.
This patch do it.

Signed-off-by: Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
---
